NAME
       jpilot - A palm pilot desktop for Linux/Unix

SYNOPSIS
       jpilot

DESCRIPTION
       J-Pilot  is  a  desktop organizer application for the palm
       pilot and other Palm OS devices.  It is similar  in  func­
       tionality to the one that 3Com distributes.

